I would suggest that the &#39;better way&#39; is to drop the drama, the insults, and the name calling.  Keep an open mind, and test claims.  If the claim is that something catastrophic is going to happen in 2012, wait and see, then decide the reliability of the source.  If the claim is that ghosts are talking on my radio, test that claim, and then decide on the reliability of those making the claim, and those disputing it.

Rj

